snippet.title: Nightgate – Trailer
snippet.description:
In the year 2398, a network of intelligent computers known as Nightgate, is the last remaining life form on Earth. Available now for iPhone, iPad and Apple TV: http://nightgate.co

Soundtrack: http://semidome.bandcamp.com/album/nightgate
